headline: ADM Recalls Select Pelleted Cattle Nutrition Feed Products
summary: CHICAGO, March 05, 2025--ADM Animal Nutrition, a division of ADM (NYSE: ADM), is recalling specific pelleted animal feed products because they may contain elevated levels of copper or have levels of zinc below the represented amounts which could be harmful to cattle.
